data.description: Have you been looking for a one story home in a cul de sac? A relaxing front porch will be a nice place to start or end your day. This floor plan offers a private study with French doors as you enter the home. An open floor plan concept that will be great for entertaining. The island kitchen has a gas stove and oven and a large pantry. The family room is spacious and has an entertainment nook that wont allow the space to impede into the family room. Master suite is at the back of home and master bath has a shower and separate tub and walk-in closet. The secondary bedrooms split from the master suite. Laundry room is spacious and  is close to secondary bedrooms. You are just minutes away from Grand Parkway,shopping and restaurants.
